text: Karavannoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Karavannensky Selsoviet, Limansky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,773 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 120 km from Astrakhan, 33 km from Liman. == References == Category:Rural localities in Limansky District
title: Karavannoye
